These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-4-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, bolivar, siglo, old-henry
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, eggplant, lemon, nectarine
City: nizza, new-york, edinburgh, miami
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, argentine, german, colombian
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, blood-red, orange, mauve
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, roller, ship, tram
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, accountant, coach, journalist
 1. the person who likes light-blue is on the far right##1
 2. the argentine is the person eating eggplant##1
 3. the person eating nectarine is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the ship is the person eating eggplant##1
 5. the coach is between the bartender and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
 6. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is the person driving the skateboard##1
 8. the montecristo-smoker is in an odd position##4
 9. the german is the bolivar-smoker##1
10. the siglo-smoker is in an even position##4
11. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the coach##3
12. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the accountant##3
13. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
14. the person eating nectarine is on the far left or far right##3
15. the polish is on the far left##1
16. the old-henry-smoker is in an odd position##4
17. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
18. the person driving the tram is the journalist##1
19. the person who likes blood-red is the person eating blueberry##1
20. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
21. the argentine is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar      | old-henry        | siglo   | montecristo         | bolivar  |
| Food          | lemon         | eggplant   | blueberry   | nectarine |
| City         | edinburgh | new-york    | miami | nizza   |
| Nationality   | polish        | argentine  | colombian      | german   |
| Color   | orange          | mauve       | blood-red        | light-blue   |
| Transport           | tram        | ship      | skateboard    | roller    |
| Job         | journalist | coach | bartender      | accountant   |

