 5. the person playing canasta is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
 8. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
10. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to new-york is the person who's birthday is in november##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the pilot##1
13. the photographer is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
15. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
16. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person playing whist##1
17. the person who's birthday is in july is in an even position##4
18. the paramedic is the person traveling to berlin##1
19. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3
