The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, thriller, western, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, snowboarding, weightlifting
City: nizza, marseilles, liverpool, hannover
 1. the siglo-smoker is between the person who likes black and the fan of funk##2
 2. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
 3. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person who growsgameade##1
 4. the fan of indie is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
 6. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who growsmarigold##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
10. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
12. the game-smoker is the person traveling to nizza##1
13. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
14. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
15. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
16. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
17. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is basketball##1
18. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
19. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |       4       |
