 8. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
 9. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4
10. the person playing poker is on the right of the bartender##1
11. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the dutch##1
12. the bartender is on the left or right of the canadian##3
13. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4
14. the game-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
15. the canadian is between the game-smoker and the person traveling to nizza##2
16. the person driving the ship is between the person who likes yellow and the journalist##2
17. the prince-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
