The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, june, july, september
City: london, edinburgh, liverpool, rome
 1. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 2. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 4. the person driving the van is in an odd position##4
 5. the person eating peas is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is the person eating peas##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
 9. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
10. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
11. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
12. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
13. the person playing canasta is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
14. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
15. the person eating peach is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person playing mah-jongg##2
16. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4
17. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
